8aec451a-7ccf-4408-a240-8e3c3c9eadb7.title: Sir Pugger
8aec451a-7ccf-4408-a240-8e3c3c9eadb7.text:
Careful traveller, this pit contains a dangerous boss,
not many know his name.

0b8395ac-5ef4-47eb-86d0-4ce86e258976.title: Sir Pugger
0b8395ac-5ef4-47eb-86d0-4ce86e258976.text:
Failing to defend the lands above from the invading
armies of the Fifth Age, the hill giants hid away"
down in these caves amongst the other beasts.

c8c64f70-1e87-42f3-9941-3e735a45e660.title: Sir Pugger
c8c64f70-1e87-42f3-9941-3e735a45e660.text:
In this pit lurks Obor. He is said to be the king
of the hill giants. His roars of anger tremble the land,
and can be felt as far away as Falador.

2e4e473f-59a3-4a0e-9fbf-b4b5a69891e8.title: <player>
2e4e473f-59a3-4a0e-9fbf-b4b5a69891e8.text: Why is he locked away down here?

632eefb3-6be1-43df-ae0f-7d6c007c6cef.title: Sir Pugger
632eefb3-6be1-43df-ae0f-7d6c007c6cef.text:
Locking himself away in the deepest part of the caves,
to keep the armies of man out. He may be plotting his
revenge on mankind.

07917257-de32-40d3-b0c1-c4e93a84d292.title: Sir Pugger
07917257-de32-40d3-b0c1-c4e93a84d292.text:
He only trusts a select few hill giants with the key
to his lair. Many adventurers have tried to defeat
him, all meeting their ill-fated end.

9697929c-e2ac-4ce2-aed6-2dd7b0fb4998.title: Sir Pugger
9697929c-e2ac-4ce2-aed6-2dd7b0fb4998.text:
I received this whip fighting mythical beasts far to
the east, inside a long forgotten tower. Overrun with
many unimaginable being's.

8dfe95c7-43e1-4624-a0f7-370d8cefe5c8.title: Sir Pugger
8dfe95c7-43e1-4624-a0f7-370d8cefe5c8.text:
That trip is a dangerous one to travel. Past the temple
on the River Salve, the tower can be found. Be wary, these
beasts are hard to kill.

b3f1e09a-608d-4a82-8351-4baa9fac3487.title: Sir Pugger
b3f1e09a-608d-4a82-8351-4baa9fac3487.text:
There have also been rumours from the castle, some are saying
have lost contact with the temple. Which could mean troubling
times ahead.

b1afff4f-7d3e-49ae-b731-e29c0c50e93b.title: Warning!
b1afff4f-7d3e-49ae-b731-e29c0c50e93b.text:
&rBe warned this is a boss instance.
&rDying will result in no gravestone.

2b255e5d-2ae6-42b4-943f-44e784eea0a6.title: Sir Pugger
2b255e5d-2ae6-42b4-943f-44e784eea0a6.text: I will need a key to open the door for you.
